"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">23</A>
Carrying the pole to measure off the camp, or clods for building the rampart, was the work of common soldiers; hence degrading for officers.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note24" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#ref24
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">24</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
