E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#ref30
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">30</A>
<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Latericiam</SPAN> is strictly "of sun-dried brick."


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note31" HREF="
