<SPAN CLASS="smallcaps">Quinquatrus</SPAN>
		</A>
in Smith's <I>Dictionary of Greek and Roman Antiquities</I>.
	</DIV>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note97" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#ref97
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">97</A>
Commonly called <SPAN CLASS="source">peperino</SPAN>, a hard grey volcanic stone with black nodules resembling peppercorns.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note98" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#ref98
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
