onMouseOut="nd();">106</A>
That is, grapes suited for eating and not for making wine; <I>cf.</I> <A HREF="
https://www.hs-augsburg.de/~harsch/Chronologia/Lspost01/Martialis/mar_xeni.html
	"TARGET="offsite"
