E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/12Caesars/Augustus*.html#ref108
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">108</A>
That is, without a blanket over his feet, because he had his shoes on.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
